1. Create a file "1.txt" as a result "ls" command on "/etc" directory. File
should be placed inside this folder "001"

2. Create a file "2.txt" as a result "ls" command on "~" directory. 
List should contain hidden files. 

3. Create a file "3.txt" as a result "ls" command on "~" directory. 
List should contain file sizes.

4. Create a file "4.txt" as a result "ls" command on "/boot" directory. 
List should be RECURSIVE.

After completions make git commit and then git push

